---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Contacto | Hablemos de tu proyecto | Davod"
  description="¿Tienes un proyecto en mente? Contacta con nuestro equipo de desarrollo web. Presupuesto gratuito y asesoramiento personalizado."
>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="pt-20">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="py-20 lg:py-32 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-dark-900 via-dark-950 to-black"></div>
      
      <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-gray-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            Hablemos de tu
          </span>
          <br>
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-400 to-primary-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            próximo proyecto
          </span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          ¿Tienes una idea brillante? ¿Necesitas mejorar tu presencia digital? 
          Estamos aquí para convertir tu visión en una realidad digital excepcional.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Content -->
    <section class="pb-20 relative">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
          <!-- Contact Info -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-1">
            <div class="bg-dark-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8 sticky top-24">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Información de contacto</h2>
              
              <!-- Contact Methods -->
              <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-600/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-1">Email</h3>
                    <a href="mailto:hola@davod.es" class="text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300 transition-colors duration-200">
                      hola@davod.es
                    </a>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Respuesta en 24h</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-600/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-1">Teléfono</h3>
                    <a href="tel:+34XXX-XXX-XXX" class="text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300 transition-colors duration-200">
                      +34 XXX XXX XXX
                    </a>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Lun-Vie 9:00-18:00</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-600/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path>
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-1">Ubicación</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300">España</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Trabajo remoto disponible</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Response Time -->
              <div class="bg-primary-600/10 border border-primary-600/20 rounded-xl p-4 mb-6">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-green-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-300">Normalmente respondemos en menos de 2 horas</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Social Links -->
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4">Síguenos</h3>
                <div class="flex space-x-3">
                  <a 
                    href="https://linkedin.com/company/davod" 
                    class="w-10 h-10 bg-dark-800 hover:bg-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-110"
                    aria-label="LinkedIn"
                  >
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.338 16.338H13.67V12.16c0-.995-.017-2.277-1.387-2.277-1.39 0-1.601 1.086-1.601 2.207v4.248H8.014v-8.59h2.559v1.174h.037c.356-.675 1.227-1.387 2.526-1.387 2.703 0 3.203 1.778 3.203 4.092v4.711zM5.005 6.575a1.548 1.548 0 11-.003-3.096 1.548 1.548 0 01.003 3.096zm-1.337 9.763H6.34v-8.59H3.667v8.59zM17.668 1H2.328C1.595 1 1 1.581 1 2.298v15.403C1 18.418 1.595 19 2.328 19h15.34c.734 0 1.332-.582 1.332-1.299V2.298C19 1.581 18.402 1 17.668 1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </a>
                  <a 
                    href="https://github.com/davod" 
                    class="w-10 h-10 bg-dark-800 hover:bg-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-110"
                    aria-label="GitHub"
                  >
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 0C4.477 0 0 4.484 0 10.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0110 4.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.203 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.942.359.31.678.921.678 1.856 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0020 10.017C20 4.484 15.522 0 10 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </a>
                  <a 
                    href="https://twitter.com/davod" 
                    class="w-10 h-10 bg-dark-800 hover:bg-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-110"
                    aria-label="Twitter"
                  >
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path d="M6.29 18.251c7.547 0 11.675-6.253 11.675-11.675 0-.178 0-.355-.012-.53A8.348 8.348 0 0020 3.92a8.19 8.19 0 01-2.357.646 4.118 4.118 0 001.804-2.27 8.224 8.224 0 01-2.605.996 4.107 4.107 0 00-6.993 3.743 11.65 11.65 0 01-8.457-4.287 4.106 4.106 0 001.27 5.477A4.073 4.073 0 01.8 7.713v.052a4.105 4.105 0 003.292 4.022 4.095 4.095 0 01-1.853.07 4.108 4.108 0 003.834 2.85A8.233 8.233 0 010 16.407a11.616 11.616 0 006.29 1.84"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Contact Form -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-2">
            <div class="bg-dark-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Envíanos un mensaje</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8">
                Cuéntanos sobre tu proyecto y te responderemos con una propuesta personalizada.
              </p>
              
              <form class="space-y-6" action="#" method="POST" id="contact-form">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                  <div>
                    <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2">
                      Nombre *
                    </label>
                    <input 
                      type="text" 
                      id="name" 
                      name="name" 
                      required
                      class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl text-white placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 focus:border-transparent transition-all duration-200"
                      placeholder="Tu nombre completo"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2">
                      Email *
                    </label>
                    <input 
                      type="email" 
                      id="email" 
                      name="email" 
                      required
                      class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl text-white placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 focus:border-transparent transition-all duration-200"
                      placeholder="tu@email.com"
                    />
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                  <div>
                    <label for="company" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2">
                      Empresa
                    </label>
                    <input 
                      type="text" 
                      id="company" 
                      name="company"
                      class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl text-white placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 focus:border-transparent transition-all duration-200"
                      placeholder="Nombre de tu empresa"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <label for="budget" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2">
                      Presupuesto estimado
                    </label>
                    <select 
                      id="budget" 
                      name="budget"
                      class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 focus:border-transparent transition-all duration-200"
                    >
                      <option value="">Seleccionar rango</option>
                      <option value="1000-5000">€1.000 - €5.000</option>
                      <option value="5000-15000">€5.000 - €15.000</option>
                      <option value="15000-50000">€15.000 - €50.000</option>
                      <option value="50000+">€50.000+</option>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                  <label for="service" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2">
                    Tipo de proyecto *
                  </label>
                  <select 
                    id="service" 
                    name="service" 
                    required
                    class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 focus:border-transparent transition-all duration-200"
                  >
                    <option value="">Seleccionar servicio</option>
                    <option value="desarrollo-web">Desarrollo Web</option>
                    <option value="app-movil">Aplicación Móvil</option>
                    <option value="diseno-ux">UI/UX Design</option>
                    <option value="consultoria">Consultoría Digital</option>
                    <option value="mantenimiento">Mantenimiento Web</option>
                    <option value="otro">Otro</option>
                  </select>
                </div>

                <div>
                  <label for="timeline" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2">
                    Timeline del proyecto
                  </label>
                  <select 
                    id="timeline" 
                    name="timeline"
                    class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 focus:border-transparent transition-all duration-200"
                  >
                    <option value="">Seleccionar timeline</option>
                    <option value="urgente">Urgente (1-2 semanas)</option>
                    <option value="rapido">Rápido (1 mes)</option>
                    <option value="normal">Normal (2-3 meses)</option>
                    <option value="flexible">Flexible (3+ meses)</option>
                  </select>
                </div>

                <div>
                  <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2">
                    Mensaje *
                  </label>
                  <textarea 
                    id="message" 
                    name="message" 
                    rows="6" 
                    required
                    class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl text-white placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 focus:border-transparent transition-all duration-200 resize-none"
                    placeholder="Cuéntanos sobre tu proyecto: objetivos, funcionalidades deseadas, público objetivo, referencias que te gusten..."
                  ></textarea>
                </div>

                <!-- Privacy Policy -->
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <input 
                    type="checkbox" 
                    id="privacy" 
                    name="privacy" 
                    required
                    class="mt-1 w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 bg-dark-800 border-gray-700 rounded focus:ring-primary-600 focus:ring-2"
                  />
                  <label for="privacy" class="text-sm text-gray-300">
                    Acepto la <a href="/privacidad" class="text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300 transition-colors duration-200">política de privacidad</a> 
                    y el tratamiento de mis datos personales. *
                  </label>
                </div>

                <button 
                  type="submit"
                  class="w-full bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary-600/25 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed"
                  id="submit-btn"
                >
                  <span id="submit-text">Enviar mensaje</span>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 inline" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 19l9 2-9-18-9 18 9-2zm0 0v-8"></path>
                  </svg>
                </button>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-dark-900/30">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Preguntas Frecuentes
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Resolvemos las dudas más comunes sobre nuestros servicios y proceso de trabajo.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-dark-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">¿Cuánto tiempo toma desarrollar un proyecto?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              El tiempo varía según la complejidad. Un sitio web básico puede tomar 2-4 semanas, 
              mientras que aplicaciones complejas pueden requerir 3-6 meses. Siempre proporcionamos 
              un timeline detallado antes de comenzar.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-dark-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">¿Ofrecen soporte post-lanzamiento?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              Sí, ofrecemos diferentes planes de soporte y mantenimiento. Incluimos 3 meses de 
              soporte gratuito con cada proyecto y planes extendidos para actualizaciones y mejoras continuas.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-dark-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">¿Trabajan con empresas internacionales?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              Absolutamente. Trabajamos con clientes de todo el mundo. Nuestro equipo está 
              acostumbrado a colaborar remotamente y adaptarse a diferentes zonas horarias.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-dark-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">¿Qué incluye el presupuesto inicial?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              Nuestros presupuestos incluyen análisis de requisitos, diseño, desarrollo, testing, 
              deployment y documentación. Los costos adicionales como hosting o licencias de terceros 
              se especifican por separado.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<script>
  // Form submission handling
  const form = document.getElementById('contact-form') as HTMLFormElement;
  const submitBtn = document.getElementById('submit-btn') as HTMLButtonElement;
  const submitText = document.getElementById('submit-text') as HTMLSpanElement;

  form?.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    
    // Update button state
    submitBtn.disabled = true;
    submitText.textContent = 'Enviando...';
    
    // Simulate form submission (replace with actual endpoint)
    setTimeout(() => {
      submitText.textContent = '¡Mensaje enviado!';
      form.reset();
      
      setTimeout(() => {
        submitBtn.disabled = false;
        submitText.textContent = 'Enviar mensaje';
      }, 2000);
    }, 1000);
  });
</script>